0 'DUAL WIELD'~
Skill Type: Active
Command: dual <weapon>

The dual wield skill allows a second weapon to be wielded in the
off-hand, though the weapon must be of equal or lighter weight.  Training
this skill makes it more likely that off-hand attacks will succeed.  Those
unfortunate enough to have only one arm are unable to use this skill.

Wielding two weapons increases the number of attacks you deal during combat
as well as with some combat skills such as backstab, and also increases the
likelihood of attacks being parried because you have two weapons with which
to try.  However, this comes at the cost of being unable to wear a shield or
hold an item in addition to your weapons, preventing the use of the shield
block skill.  

If you are disarmed while dual-wielding, you will automatically switch your
off-hand weapon to your main hand in order to continue fighting.  
~

